  • Constructor Details

    • Card

      public Card​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String color, java.lang.String suit, int rank)
      Constructor to set the attributes of a card for the Euchre game.
      Parameters:
      name - Name of the Card. Ex. King
      color - What color the card is (Black or Red).
      suit - What suit the card is (Diamonds, Hearts, Clubs, Spades).
      rank - What rank the card is depending on what the current trump card is.
